name: Image have alt attribute ?
description: Images should have alt attribute, it can be empty or contain text

name: Image have alt attribute override by something else ?
description: Images tag must use alt attribute, not any other way such as aria-label, title etc

name: Is navigation is present ?
description: primary navigation is required, it help a lot to quickly identify which page can be visited

name: Does all Frames have a title ?
description: When you have iframe on your page, you should add title attribute which describe your iframe

name: DescribeBy refer to a valid id ?
description: when you use describedBy, you should refer to a valid id, present on the page

name: Do we have multiple describer at once ?
description: there is multiple labelling, we should use only once per element to avoid different behavior of the browser.

name: aria-hidden-focus
description: Ensures aria-hidden elements do not contain focusable elements

name: aria-required-attr
description: Ensures elements with ARIA roles have all required ARIA attributes

name: aria-required-children
description: Ensures elements with an ARIA role that require child roles contain them

name: aria-required-parent
description: Ensures elements with an ARIA role that require parent roles are contained by them

name: aria-roles
description: Ensures all elements with a role attribute use a valid value

description: Ensures all ARIA attributes have valid values

description: Ensures attributes that begin with aria- are valid ARIA attributes

description: Ensures buttons have discernible text

name: bypass

description: Ensures each HTML document contains a non-empty <title> element
